Human Language: english
>Description:
In the DrS About box, there's a pointer to the 
COPYING-LIB file in the local filesystem.  With the 
About box at normal size, the path gets broken
over two lines, which looks kind of naff.

I think it would be better to have a link to the
servlet /servlets/release/license.ss, which contains
somewhat more info than the GNU file, and also has 
a link to the GNU file.



>How-To-Repeat:
Start the DrS About box.
